{"tid":17941,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔開心","createTime":"2016-12-02T04:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T01:37:45.000Z","uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b5c52f80b35f3062654569e0b42ba8d1cf1cba","tid":17941,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"我覺得自己好撚無用，又蠢，又懶<br />\n<br />\n又容易諗埋一邊，經常都有諗過自殺，但一諗到身邊既人，我就落唔到手⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n但日日loop負能量真係好辛苦，每日都要扮開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce20f642e7bca81689ee85f5be8910f2d400b1d3","tid":17941,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:34:01.000Z","msg":"不如講多少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔係成日都會係到<br />\n但都可以夠你傾陣計"},{"pid":"fe7b7cf73f4d66b2239bc8f82b2f53e9706c405c","tid":17941,"uid":26860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"盡訴心中情，請講咩事"},{"pid":"1cef3d89ceaae3f355a87945664cd8651df3eb42","tid":17941,"uid":42957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:51:28.000Z","msg":"講出黎  舒服d"},{"pid":"377cf949195774b408943b38454b7bc441a18220","tid":17941,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"多謝兩位巴打既關心<br />\n<br />\n我好奇怪，由細到大都會亂諗野，好易諗埋一邊<br />\n<br />\n所以好難講因爲咩事而唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n最近經常都覺得自己無用、廢、麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a7571d31b75deaedb6941d6eff808e2162560c","tid":17941,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:59:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝兩位巴打既關心<br />\n<br />\n我好奇怪，由細到大都會亂諗野，好易諗埋一邊<br />\n<br />\n所以好難講因爲咩事而唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n最近經常都覺得自己無用、廢、麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁不如講下你自己既野呀<br />\n例如讀緊書定做緊野 ? <br />\n平時會唔會有啲哂興趣咁<br />\n<br />\n唔洗急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874e6102625816bbdcba5df037af9c96208d836c","tid":17941,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:40:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多謝兩位巴打既關心<br />\n<br />\n我好奇怪，由細到大都會亂諗野，好易諗埋一邊<br />\n<br />\n所以好難講因爲咩事而唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n最近經常都覺得自己無用、廢、麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁不如講下你自己既野呀<br />\n例如讀緊書定做緊野 ? <br />\n平時會唔會有啲哂興趣咁<br />\n<br />\n唔洗急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返緊份濕鳩工，暫時既收入都可觀，但呢行前景唔明朗，想轉行（連d前輩都想轉），但唔知轉咩好。<br />\n<br />\n興趣就打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769c24a2da5b37f93c4de7eb73742cb5b3c03158","tid":17941,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但路仍然要行"},{"pid":"752b0227190a553a8b1a54e6a1b0a83fc137ef10","tid":17941,"uid":34404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"加油呀龜龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80bd202d6b68eea8121740a2e73332a26bbb45e0","tid":17941,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>多謝兩位巴打既關心<br />\n<br />\n我好奇怪，由細到大都會亂諗野，好易諗埋一邊<br />\n<br />\n所以好難講因爲咩事而唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n最近經常都覺得自己無用、廢、麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁不如講下你自己既野呀<br />\n例如讀緊書定做緊野 ? <br />\n平時會唔會有啲哂興趣咁<br />\n<br />\n唔洗急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返緊份濕鳩工，暫時既收入都可觀，但呢行前景唔明朗，想轉行（連d前輩都想轉），但唔知轉咩好。<br />\n<br />\n興趣就打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返咩工呀，我宜家份工都濕鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過諗住做埋呢年儲錢，之後開鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02f444cd1373412f1d12df86b45743006251424","tid":17941,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>多謝兩位巴打既關心<br />\n<br />\n我好奇怪，由細到大都會亂諗野，好易諗埋一邊<br />\n<br />\n所以好難講因爲咩事而唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n最近經常都覺得自己無用、廢、麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁不如講下你自己既野呀<br />\n例如讀緊書定做緊野 ? <br />\n平時會唔會有啲哂興趣咁<br />\n<br />\n唔洗急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返緊份濕鳩工，暫時既收入都可觀，但呢行前景唔明朗，想轉行（連d前輩都想轉），但唔知轉咩好。<br />\n<br />\n興趣就打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返咩工呀，我宜家份工都濕鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過諗住做埋呢年儲錢，之後開鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一份無前景既工，講黎都無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821b601c7ab8b633df0b33a0ad38d53dd1797aa5","tid":17941,"uid":42957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:54:26.000Z","msg":"做下運動 再沖個涼 訓醒 又係另一條好漢"},{"pid":"6d4afc45ab8569377145e3b9e6114e6fa2796959","tid":17941,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:37:45.000Z","msg":"冇事既"}]}